Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:20.00,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}我發著呆 凝望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:24.16,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}你是否 還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:30.72,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}那些錯過的季節 不確定的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:38.76,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}即便只能深藏於心 若能化為碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:48.17,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}你的笑容猶在即好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:52.19,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}若時光飛逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:56.16,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}若能與你一起
